The Audi technician CARFAX skill is specifically designed for the Audi brand technician to access vehicle history and current status of the vehicle using this skill. This skill is to be used only in the workshop by an authorized Audi technician.

CarFax Vehicle History Reports are products of CarFax, Inc. See www.carfax.com/vehicle-history-reports/ for complete details about such reports, including the data contained therein.
